data.description: MOVE-IN READY! Winner of 2014 National Builder of the Year Award, This Duvall B plan has it all! Two stories of maximum usable space with gorgeous paneled foyer, amazing master suite w/sitting room, first floor guest room, 3 car garage, organization room, butler's pantry, total of 5BR and bonus! NO CARPET! Enjoy LVP, hardwood stairs, wall treatments, beauty and crown molding, coffered ceilings, mud bench, and more. This home is located on one of our premier backline lots, which has only woods between you and the Flint River. The energy program in our homes is on the cutting edge of efficiency, affordability, and convenience.
data.whatILove: Covered and screened patio. Whole house generator. Storm shelter in garage.
